This repository provides an implementation of the Dynamic Multi-Party Homomorphic Encryption (dMPHE) and Reusable Dynamic Multi-Party Homomorphic Encryption (rdMPHE) schemes represented in a CiC submission. This library is built upon (https://github.com/SNUCP/snu-mghe, from https://github.com/SNUCP/MKHE-KKLSS) and Lattigo v2.3.0(https://github.com/tuneinsight/lattigo/tree/v2.3.0).


LICENSE
===============
Attribution-NonCommercial 2.0 Generic (CC BY-NC 2.0)

HOW TO INSTALL
==============
use "go mod vendor" 

HOW TO RUN
====================
1. go to target folder (e.g for mkckks "cd mkckks")
2. run go benchmark command "go test -timeout=0 -args -n=1" (This runs 10 repetition of benchmark)

